    "What this suggests is that the use of REST does not particularly penalize MCP.",
    "It does, however introduce its own overheads that are evident in purple in Figure 8.",
    "In comparing REST (Figure 6 and native MCP 7, one can see sizeable overheads in the wide area setting for Edge Create.",
